","tid":886021,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8abff1e8dcc64f7493f86d6e9f8196def3a66a1","tid":886021,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e486b45db6f99b97a1d08ce7b7543ee68a63798","tid":886021,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:47:07.000Z","msg":"Yield最主要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"唔係 搞錯 應該係政治因素"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:20:59.000Z","msg":"details?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"例如希臘債務危機出現<br />\n市場反應會導致個債券價格下跌<br />\nYield 就上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b2091dd856e21b21cf3a31888bef9e6c04676f","tid":886021,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"972f963b4f0f478d82d92e0e6fa2dcac362fe502","tid":886021,"uid":87737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78e00e7e8c2b458e3808b908d652a5c9e0ece06","tid":886021,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3cacfc1e97701b2d846220804a6d2ffe1fabd7b","tid":886021,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"漫步華爾街話利率上升，債券就會跌，因為市場會有新既高息債券推出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"簡單經濟學，借貸成本提高<br />\n專業投資者主要係賺取息差<br />\n而同一項投資品<br />\n其風險水平、及回報吸引力下降<br />\n所以被沽售，直到Yield升至有吸引力嘅位置"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n短線利息上升都會因為咁而影響到長期利率上升"},{"pid":"8a8cd5c85714a0d11716abd3098509a78b948f8c","tid":886021,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"樓主啲文高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過如果可以寫啲實用性高啲嘅題目就更加好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\neg. 行業估值計算、資產管理策略、辨別趨勢技術形態、落盤技巧 etc."}]}